		<p>A disclosure toggles the visibility of another element. Add class <code>.fb-disclosure</code> to a link, and a target element in the <code>href</code>.</p>

		<div class="example">

	   		<a class="fb-disclosure" href="#disclosed-1">Disclose Stuff</a>
			<div id="disclosed-1" style="display: none">
